msgctxt "text"
msgid "You have now completed @(fields.c_n_mod_compl +1) out of @fields.c_n_mod lessons in the course, Understand Development of Girls and Boys. ⭐"
msgstr "Completaste @(fields.c_n_mod_compl +1) de las @fields.c_n_mod sesiones del curso Entender el Desarrollo de las Niñas y los Niños. ⭐"

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎨 Playing with @fields.child_nickname is important for their development and learning in and out of school. This is true for ALL girls and boys, including those with physical and developmental disabilities. "
msgstr "🎨 Jugar con @fields.child_nickname es importante para su desarrollo y aprendizaje dentro y fuera de la escuela. Esto es una realidad para TODAS las niñas y TODOS los niños, incluidos los que tienen discapacidades físicas y del desarrollo. "

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚲 Did you know that playing also helps @fields.child_nickname learn social values and social rules?"
msgstr "🚲 ¿Sabías que jugar también le ayuda a @fields.child_nickname a aprender valores y normas sociales?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎨 Playing with your {child} is important for their development and learning in and out of school. This is true for ALL girls and boys, including those with physical and developmental disabilities. "
