#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Your Home Activity today is to praise @fields.child_nickname for one thing you’d like them to keep doing. If @fields.child_nickname refuses to follow instructions or forgets a household rule, you can use a consequence that is connected to the behaviour. Remember it is important to be fair, consistent, and calm when you give a consequence."
