msgid "How can you help your {teen} feel better about themselves when they feel that they’ve made a mistake or failed?"
msgstr "¿Cómo puedes ayudar a tu {teen} a sentirse mejor con su persona cuando siente que ha cometido un error o que fracasó?"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀Your teen is always learning from you, even when it doesn’t seem like it. "
msgstr "👀 Tu adolescente siempre está aprendiendo de ti, aunque no lo parezca. "

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
