#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😣 Trying to be perfect all the time can make @fields.child_nickname feel under pressure. Avoiding challenges so they don’t make mistakes may not let @fields.child_nickname learn and grow. "
