msgid "💙Having hope makes @fields.child_nickname feel better about the future. It helps them feel comfortable setting goals and working towards them. It also makes them less afraid to think about what will happen. \r\r💛If @fields.child_nickname is not feeling hopeful about their future, they can feel unsure and worried about what will happen next. This will also discourage them from planning their future and setting goals."
